@gillianoberholzer @yasserogier @cobuspienaar 
Hi guys,

Experian acknowledges that they did not specify passports numbers up front. However, they would now like to know the possibility and possible issues relating to putting the passport number in the ID number field when a passport number exists and the ID number does not exist? If you don't foresee any issues, a separate log will be submitted for this as Experian's dev will need to make changes on their side as well.
